{"type": "article", "id": 14780, "title": "智能笔记本", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-11T07:11:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 31, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003284Tqykb3OvXMa6fCS.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t日本 WACOM 公司推出一款智能笔记本 Bamboo Spark ，携带一支Bamboo Spark智能圆珠笔。使用者一边在纸上涂写，另一边直接保存到云端，然后转到移动设备的配套应用上，方便随时查看。Bamboo Spark 适用于所有智能手机和平板电脑，有三种不同款式可供选择：配备小工具口袋；配备数位板包套；配备iPad Air 2 卡扣。<a href=\"http://evernote.com/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142230ZsKIUG2WYP7uCVn6.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"387\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.47310513\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261422313RfaYnSew0sMvKN8.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"500\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142231OIND12LSheBtgZzi.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"545\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}